@startuml State Chart Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

[*] --> CoverMode

state CoverMode as "Cover Feed Mode"
state ChatMode as "Hidden Chat Mode"

CoverMode --> ChatMode : Triple-click header\n(secret trigger)
ChatMode --> CoverMode : Triple-click header\n(secret trigger)

state "Settings Modal" as Settings
ChatMode --> Settings : Click settings button
Settings --> ChatMode : Save & Close

state "Typing" as Typing
ChatMode --> Typing : User starts typing
Typing --> ChatMode : Timeout (2s) or Send

state "Processing" as Processing
ChatMode --> Processing : Click Send
Processing --> ChatMode : Encoding complete\nor Error

note right of CoverMode
    Displays images as
    social media feed
end note

note right of ChatMode
    Shows encrypted chat
    with steganographic messages
end note

note right of Processing
    Encrypts, encodes,
    sends message
end note
@enduml
